<BaseLayout title="How to Describe Poses Clearly" description="Learn readable pose prompt language for AI image generation." canonicalPath="/guides/pose-prompts/"><article class="content-section article-body"><h1>How to Describe Poses Clearly</h1><p>Pose prompts should describe body position and direction plainly: standing, sitting, kneeling, walking, reaching, turning, or looking over shoulder. Add balance and silhouette notes when the pose is important.</p><p>Avoid asking for standing and sitting, close-up and full body, or front view and back view at the same time. Contradictions make the model guess.</p></article></BaseLayout>
